to.sven.androidrccar.common.logic.impl

Class AbstractLogic<TDependencyContainer extends IDependencyContainer<? extends IFactory,TListener>,TListener extends ILogicListener>

  • java.lang.Object
    • to.sven.androidrccar.common.logic.impl.AbstractLogic<TDependencyContainer,TListener>
  • Type Parameters:
    TDependencyContainer - A concrete IDependencyContainer interface for dependency injection.
    TListener - The concrete type of a ILogicListener, that uses this Logic (Most likely an Activity).
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRemoteCommunicationListener, ILogic, ILogicHandlerFacade<TDependencyContainer>

    public abstract class AbstractLogic<TDependencyContainer extends IDependencyContainer<? extends IFactory,TListener>,TListener extends ILogicListener>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRemoteCommunicationListener, ILogicHandlerFacade<TDependencyContainer>, ILogic
    General implementation for Host and Client. It provides the relaying of incoming message to the concrete IMessageHandler and error handling. (On an error the connection will be closed.)
    Author:
    sven
